</Output>
</Group><Text-field style="Normal" layout="Normal">To see the reason for this, just expand out <Equation executable="false" style="2D Comment" input-equation="" display=""></Equation>.  The leading term is <Equation executable="false" style="2D Comment" input-equation="" display="LUklbXJvd0c2Iy9JK21vZHVsZW5hbWVHNiJJLFR5cGVzZXR0aW5nR0koX3N5c2xpYkdGJzYmLUkjbWlHRiQ2JVEhRicvJSdpdGFsaWNHUSV0cnVlRicvJSxtYXRodmFyaWFudEdRJ2l0YWxpY0YnLUYjNiQtSSVtc3VwR0YkNiUtRiw2JVEieEYnRi9GMi1JI21uR0YkNiRRIjdGJy9GM1Enbm9ybWFsRicvJTFzdXBlcnNjcmlwdHNoaWZ0R1EiMEYnRkFGK0ZB">LUklbXJvd0c2Iy9JK21vZHVsZW5hbWVHNiJJLFR5cGVzZXR0aW5nR0koX3N5c2xpYkdGJzYmLUkjbWlHRiQ2JVEhRicvJSdpdGFsaWNHUSV0cnVlRicvJSxtYXRodmFyaWFudEdRJ2l0YWxpY0YnLUYjNiQtSSVtc3VwR0YkNiUtRiw2JVEieEYnRi9GMi1JI21uR0YkNiRRIjdGJy9GM1Enbm9ybWFsRicvJTFzdXBlcnNjcmlwdHNoaWZ0R1EiMEYnRkFGK0ZB</Equation>, and the remaining terms are multiples of <Equation executable="false" style="2D Comment" input-equation="" display="LUklbXJvd0c2Iy9JK21vZHVsZW5hbWVHNiJJLFR5cGVzZXR0aW5nR0koX3N5c2xpYkdGJzYmLUkjbWlHRiQ2JVEhRicvJSdpdGFsaWNHUSV0cnVlRicvJSxtYXRodmFyaWFudEdRJ2l0YWxpY0YnLUYjNiQtSSVtc3VwR0YkNiUtRiw2JVEieEYnRi9GMi1JI21uR0YkNiRRIjVGJy9GM1Enbm9ybWFsRicvJTFzdXBlcnNjcmlwdHNoaWZ0R1EiMEYnRkFGK0ZB">LUklbXJvd0c2Iy9JK21vZHVsZW5hbWVHNiJJLFR5cGVzZXR0aW5nR0koX3N5c2xpYkdGJzYmLUkjbWlHRiQ2JVEhRicvJSdpdGFsaWNHUSV0cnVlRicvJSxtYXRodmFyaWFudEdRJ2l0YWxpY0YnLUYjNiQtSSVtc3VwR0YkNiUtRiw2JVEieEYnRi9GMi1JI21uR0YkNiRRIjVGJy9GM1Enbm9ybWFsRicvJTFzdXBlcnNjcmlwdHNoaWZ0R1EiMEYnRkFGK0ZB</Equation> or lower, so they are much smaller than <Equation executable="false" style="2D Comment" input-equation="" display="LUklbXJvd0c2Iy9JK21vZHVsZW5hbWVHNiJJLFR5cGVzZXR0aW5nR0koX3N5c2xpYkdGJzYmLUkjbWlHRiQ2JVEhRicvJSdpdGFsaWNHUSV0cnVlRicvJSxtYXRodmFyaWFudEdRJ2l0YWxpY0YnLUYjNiQtSSVtc3VwR0YkNiUtRiw2JVEieEYnRi9GMi1JI21uR0YkNiRRIjdGJy9GM1Enbm9ybWFsRicvJTFzdXBlcnNjcmlwdHNoaWZ0R1EiMEYnRkFGK0ZB">LUklbXJvd0c2Iy9JK21vZHVsZW5hbWVHNiJJLFR5cGVzZXR0aW5nR0koX3N5c2xpYkdGJzYmLUkjbWlHRiQ2JVEhRicvJSdpdGFsaWNHUSV0cnVlRicvJSxtYXRodmFyaWFudEdRJ2l0YWxpY0YnLUYjNiQtSSVtc3VwR0YkNiUtRiw2JVEieEYnRi9GMi1JI21uR0YkNiRRIjdGJy9GM1Enbm9ybWFsRicvJTFzdXBlcnNjcmlwdHNoaWZ0R1EiMEYnRkFGK0ZB</Equation> when <Equation executable="false" style="2D Comment" input-equation="" display="LUklbXJvd0c2Iy9JK21vZHVsZW5hbWVHNiJJLFR5cGVzZXR0aW5nR0koX3N5c2xpYkdGJzYkLUkjbWlHRiQ2JVEieEYnLyUnaXRhbGljR1EldHJ1ZUYnLyUsbWF0aHZhcmlhbnRHUSdpdGFsaWNGJy9GM1Enbm9ybWFsRic=">LUklbXJvd0c2Iy9JK21vZHVsZW5hbWVHNiJJLFR5cGVzZXR0aW5nR0koX3N5c2xpYkdGJzYkLUkjbWlHRiQ2JVEieEYnLyUnaXRhbGljR1EldHJ1ZUYnLyUsbWF0aHZhcmlhbnRHUSdpdGFsaWNGJy9GM1Enbm9ybWFsRic=</Equation> is large.</Text-field>
