</Output>
</Group><Text-field style="Normal" layout="Normal"><Font size="14" style="Text" bold="true">(a)</Font> Most of the time the graph is very flat, and close to <Equation executable="false" style="2D Comment" input-equation="" display=""></Equation>.  Somewhere close to <Equation executable="false" style="2D Comment" input-equation="" display=""></Equation>, the graph climbs steeply to <Equation executable="false" style="2D Comment" input-equation="" display="LUklbXJvd0c2Iy9JK21vZHVsZW5hbWVHNiJJLFR5cGVzZXR0aW5nR0koX3N5c2xpYkdGJzYkLUkjbWlHRiQ2JVEoJiM4NzM0O0YnLyUnaXRhbGljR1EmZmFsc2VGJy8lLG1hdGh2YXJpYW50R1Enbm9ybWFsRidGMg==">LUklbXJvd0c2Iy9JK21vZHVsZW5hbWVHNiJJLFR5cGVzZXR0aW5nR0koX3N5c2xpYkdGJzYkLUkjbWlHRiQ2JVEoJiM4NzM0O0YnLyUnaXRhbGljR1EmZmFsc2VGJy8lLG1hdGh2YXJpYW50R1Enbm9ybWFsRidGMg==</Equation>, jumps down discontinuously to <Equation executable="false" style="2D Comment" input-equation="" display=""></Equation>, and then climbs back up to around <Equation executable="false" style="2D Comment" input-equation="" display="LUklbXJvd0c2Iy9JK21vZHVsZW5hbWVHNiJJLFR5cGVzZXR0aW5nR0koX3N5c2xpYkdGJzYkLUkjbW5HRiQ2JFEkMC43RicvJSxtYXRodmFyaWFudEdRJ25vcm1hbEYnRi8=">LUklbXJvd0c2Iy9JK21vZHVsZW5hbWVHNiJJLFR5cGVzZXR0aW5nR0koX3N5c2xpYkdGJzYkLUkjbW5HRiQ2JFEkMC43RicvJSxtYXRodmFyaWFudEdRJ25vcm1hbEYnRi8=</Equation> again.</Text-field>
